all holding the official swords.

42
00:02:18,130 --> 00:02:21,250
[Official sword]

43
00:02:23,480 --> 00:02:24,430
Be careful next time.

44
00:02:25,920 --> 00:02:27,800
Even swords are not the key.

45
00:02:28,420 --> 00:02:28,970
